<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT61">
<l>maṉakkētañ cārā matucūtaṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>taṉakkētāṉ tañcamāk koḷḷi leṉakkētā</l>
<l>ṉiṉṟoṉṟi niṉṟulakai yēḻāṇai yōṭṭiṉāṉ</l>
<l>ceṉṟoṉṟi niṉṟa tiru.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Afflictions of the mind will not approach</l>
<l>If one accepts Madhusūdana as the refuge for oneself.</l>
<l>Today, He who ruled the seven worlds remaining together</l>
<l>came [to me]. The wealth remains as one [with me] is only for me!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
